originalText.text: M & J is my hidden gem in the city for takeout sushi. Their 3 roll combo always comes with fluffy rice, great quality fish, and is picked up with ease for me every time. And you cannot beat the price for the quality anywhere else in the city. Couldn’t recommend this place more!

originalText.text: Ordered beef fried rice and chicken wings on DoorDash. The chicken wings were alright and the beef fried rice was bland. I was eating the rice when I noticed something hard and sharp in my mouth. I spit it out and it was a rusty paper clip. I searched through the rice and saw many more hidden inside. Never go here. Disgusting

originalText.text:
My go to Chinese food. Quick order if you pickup in person.
We always get the sesame chicken, crab wontons, chicken fried rice and vegetable fried rice. Ocassionally we'll order the bento box (katsu - chicken is super thin though) and sushi which is good.

originalText.text: I came here  as a delivery person to pick up an order for a customer. I showed them the order on my phone, they turned over the order they then asked me to confirm. They insisted that I show them me starting the delivery which is a violation of the customers privacy and grounds for my deactivation. They continued to ask and harass me to start the delivery. I refused to show them my phone cause it’s my phone, and they can’t deputize and micromanage my property. They proceeded to follow me out side like a gang, to “retrieve” the order. One of the men literally started grabbing at my backpack, and sizing  me up to fight. One woman put her legs between my bike so I couldn’t escape this horrible situation. I called the cops and they got their food back and I lost out on a trip. That customers food probably got cold by the time that delivery got canceled. They were not professional, they were thugs! I reported them right afterwards. Even the cops said they were in the wrong. They have no decorum or remorse. Uber and door dash delivery drivers kept your business going when the city shut down and you repay us by hostility and physical aggression. Do not support this business as a courier or a customer. They are terrible !
